high_descs: Turn left and walk to the tissue box next to the lamp on the desk.
Pick up the tissue box to the left of the lamp.
Turn left and walk to the small table with keys on it.
Place the tissue box on the shelf just below the keys.
Turn right and walk to tissue box on the desk.
Pick up the box of tissues.
Turn left and walk to the small table with keys on it.
Place the tissue box next to the other tissue box on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place two tissue boxes on the shelf just below the keys on the small table.

high_descs: Turn left, turn left again, walk towards book case, turn right walk to the desk
pick up tissue form left hand corner of the desk
turn right, turn right again, turn right one more time to face the small cabinet in front of you
place the tissue on the middle shelf on the small cabinet in front of you
turn right, turn right again, face the desk in front of you
pick up the remaining box of tissue from the desk
turn right, turn right again, turn right one more time to face the small cabinet in front of you
place the box of tissue on the middle shelf of the small cabinet in front of you next to the box of tissue already there
anns.task_desc: to get both boxes of tissue off of desk putting them on the small cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and go to the desk.
Pick up the box of tissues on the far left of the desk.
Turn around and face the shorter shelf.
Put the box of tissues on the middle shelf.
Turn around and go back to the desk.
Pick up the second box of tissues on the desk.
Turn around and face the shorter shelf again.
Put the box of tissues on the middle shelf to the right of the first.
anns.task_desc: Put two tissue boxes on the short shelf.

high_descs: turn around, go straight to the book case, turn right, go straight to the desk.
Take the tissue box on the left of the desk.
Turn left to face the stand to the right of the book case.
Put the tissue box on the left side of the lower shelf of the stand.
Turn right and go to the desk.
Take the tissue box from the desk.
Turn left to face the stand to the right of the book case.
Put the tissue box on the right side of the first tissue box on the lower shelf of the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put two tissues boxes on a stand.

high_descs: Turn around and go towards the book shelves, then turn to the right and go to the desk with the chair at it.
Pick up the box of tissues that is on the desk to the left of the lamp.
Turn around to the small table that is on the right of the book shelves.
Put the box of tissues on the left side of the shelf that is under the keys.
Turn to the right and go back to the desk.
Pick up the box of tissues that is on the desk.
Turn around to the small table that is on the right of the book shelves.
Put the box of tissues on the shelf directly to the right of the other box of tissues.
anns.task_desc: Put two boxes of tissues on a shelf.
